The '''Imperial Outer Rim Territories Patrol Fleet''' was a [[Capital ship/Legends|capital ship]] [[Fleet/Legends|fleet]] of the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] assigned to patrol and respond to threats in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]].

==History==
Early in the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], prior to the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]] and shortly thereafter, the [[Fleet/Legends|fleet]] was commanded by [[Bane Nothos]] until his capture at the hands of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] and subsequent death.

